---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy"
  description="Wander Tiger privacy policy for analytics, ads, affiliate links, and contact information."
  current="none"
>
  <section class="hero-panel nes-container is-dark with-title">
    <p class="title">PRIVACY</p>
    <p class="nes-text is-disabled kicker">DATA · ANALYTICS · COOKIES</p>
    <h1 class="nes-text is-primary page-title hero-title">PRIVACY POLICY</h1>
    <p class="nes-text hero-copy">
      This page explains what information Wander Tiger may collect as the site
      grows and monetization features are added.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="nes-container is-dark with-title section-gap">
    <p class="title">CURRENT STATE</p>
    <p class="nes-text is-disabled compact-copy">
      Wander Tiger is a static Astro website hosted on Cloudflare Pages. The
      site does not currently require user accounts, payments, or login details.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="nes-container is-dark with-title section-gap">
    <p class="title">POSSIBLE DATA</p>
    <div class="console-list">
      <div class="console-row">
        <span class="console-index">01</span>
        <p class="nes-text is-disabled">
          Hosting providers may collect basic technical logs such as IP address,
          browser type, requested pages, timestamps, and error logs.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="console-row">
        <span class="console-index">02</span>
        <p class="nes-text is-disabled">
          If analytics, AdSense, or affiliate tracking are added later, third
          parties may use cookies or similar technologies to measure traffic,
          conversions, and ad performance.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="console-row">
        <span class="console-index">03</span>
        <p class="nes-text is-disabled">
          If a newsletter, contact form, or downloadable template is added, the
          site may collect information you voluntarily submit, such as your name
          or email address.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="nes-container is-dark with-title section-gap">
    <p class="title">YOUR CHOICES</p>
    <p class="nes-text is-disabled compact-copy">
      You can block cookies through your browser settings. You can also avoid
      submitting personal information if optional forms or downloads are added in
      the future.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
